*ncmpc-0.12_beta2 (28 Nov 2008)

  28 Nov 2008; David Shakaryan <omp@gentoo.org> metadata.xml,
  +ncmpc-0.12_beta2.ebuild:
  Version bump; finally a new release.

  28 Nov 2008; David Shakaryan <omp@gentoo.org> -ncmpc-0.11.0.ebuild,
  -ncmpc-0.11.1.ebuild, -ncmpc-0.11.1-r1.ebuild:
  Remove older versions.

  22 Sep 2008; David Shakaryan <omp@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add myself as the maintainer of media-sound/ncmpc.

  30 May 2008; Christian Heim <phreak@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Removing Andrej Kacian (Ticho) from metadata.xml (as per #59986).

  09 Oct 2007; Christoph Mende <angelos@gentoo.org> ncmpc-0.11.1-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on amd64 wrt bug #193881

  06 Oct 2007; Tobias Scherbaum <dertobi123@gentoo.org>
  ncmpc-0.11.1-r2.ebuild:
  ppc stable, bug #193881

  03 Oct 2007; Ferris McCormick <fmccor@gentoo.org> ncmpc-0.11.1-r2.ebuild:
  Sparc stable --- Bug #193881 --- thanks to Friedrich Oslage.

  02 Oct 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> ncmpc-0.11.1-r2.ebuild:
  Stable on x86, bug #193881.

  26 Sep 2007; Jeroen Roovers <jer@gentoo.org> ncmpc-0.11.1-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for HPPA (Unicode support, bug #193881).

  01 May 2007; Marius Mauch <genone@gentoo.org> ncmpc-0.11.1-r1.ebuild,
  ncmpc-0.11.1-r2.ebuild:
  Replacing einfo with elog

  04 Apr 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> ncmpc-0.11.1-r2.ebuild:
  Only apply patch to use libncursesw for wide chars if ncurses has been built
  with unicode support. Bug #155177, suggested by Mathias Gumz <akira at
  fluxbox.org>.

*ncmpc-0.11.1-r2 (28 Mar 2007)

